DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages java
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include java              # Install and run java with standard configurations.
include java::disable     # Disable java service.
include java::disableboot # Disable java service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include java::absent      # Remove java package.

DEPENDENCIES:
